description: East side living, but renovated in 2012. Very spacious, natural light filled home on charming City Point street.  Desirable and ideal locale nearby M Street beach for enjoying salt air and summer breezes. This fantastic condo offers a flexible floor plan adaptable for your specific requirements. Enjoy an extension of main area via private tree top composite deck perfect for Al fresco dining or just unwinding.  A lovely gas fireplace anchors the space adding ambience.Hardwood floors throughout the home and kitchen boasts stainless appliances (new dishwasher) and timeless quality wood cabinetry. In unit laundry will simplify life.  Primary bedroom features 3 windows and may hold king bed with abundant closet space. Very generous size bedrooms. Central air & enormous additional storage for keepsakes.   Bring your furry companion along for exploring this A plus neighborhood, with abundant transit options, dining, shopping, entertainment (new Park City).
